Help chests

Chests are used to save equipment over boots and while player is
not online. Normal chests store upto ten equipment. Chests save
equipment only when closed. If someone manages to force chest
open, it becomes ruined and must be repaired for to be useable
again. Ruined chests don't save. Chests can be bought from castle
shop at (not yet).

Chests can be transported only as open, unsealed and empty.

Commands:

turn <chest> to <num>
open <chest>
close <chest>
recode <chest> to <num>
seal <chest>
unseal <chest>
label <chest> as <label>
force <chest>
info <chest>

See also 'help castles'
